- All signal data is Float32Array of samples
- Keep DSP math in /utils/dsp.ts (pure functions, no side effects)
- Keep chart components in /components/charts/
- react-native-gifted-charts for all signal plots (no Skia dependency, stable on Windows/Web)
- Use custom hooks (useSignal, useFilter, useFFT) to separate logic from UI
- Never do heavy computation on the JS thread — use useMemo and batch updates
- All screens must work offline
- TypeScript strict mode on
- Write clear comments on any DSP math
